# Clinic Management System - Cursor Agent Rules

## Project Context

**Multi-tenant healthcare web app** for medical clinics (all specialties)  
**Tech Stack**: Vite (React + TypeScript), Tailwind CSS, Shadcn UI, Supabase (RLS + MCP), Google OAuth, React Query, zod, Twilio, Resend  
**Critical Requirements**: Strict multi-tenancy, role-based access (superadmin, doctor, staff), HIPAA compliance, DPDT compliance (India)
**Development Tools**: Supabase MCP for database operations, schema management, and RLS testing. Playwright MCP to access browser console, take page screenshots, navigate the web, fill out forms, and click on buttons etc..


