## 🏥 Healthcare-Specific Rules

### HIPAA Compliance
- No PHI in logs or error messages
- All data access audited through RLS
- Encryption for sensitive fields

### Role-Based Access
- `superadmin`: Full clinic management
- `doctor`: Patient records, appointments
- `staff`: Scheduling, basic patient info

### Data Integrity
- Cascade deletes for clinic relationships
- Audit trails for sensitive operations
- Regular cross-clinic leak detection

